OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fstart with clear spells, then turning
OL,7,Fcloudy through the evening with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain, which continue
OL,9,Fovernight and may be heavy at times.
OL,10,FBreezy, strong winds near coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with heavy and often
OL,13,Fpersistent outbreaks of rain. Winds
OL,14,Fbecoming strong across all parts with
OL,15,Fa risk of gales, especially near
OL,16,Fcoasts. Driest, brightest towards
OL,17,FInverness and Nairn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
