OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,8,FTuesday. Mostly cloudy Wednesday with
OL,9,Fheavy rain at times. Winds light
OL,10,FMonday then breezy on Tuesday and
OL,11,FWednesday.
